hackathon-eligibility: Only participants 18 yrs or older can participate.  They must be members of a team of at least 3 members, and no more than 5 members.  Must be present to participate, submit, and win.
hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=21 Drydock Ave, Boston, MA 02210, USA

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: Target audience is clearly defined, needs are well identified, marketing plan addresses this audience creatively.  App design matches needs of this audience, launch plan is thorough. Sustainability and monetization are realistically addressed.
The idea seems extremely feasible and viable with a high probability of success.

Design of application is very user friendly.  Application is strongly designed and features implemented have a realistic application. Solution was creative and addressed most of the special considerations.

hackathon-description-header: Create a mobile app to help adults manage their emotional health
